### 4. Sharing & Public Benchmarks

We believe in the performance of Busbar and encourage you to discuss it with your peers. To ensure accuracy and context during this early phase, we ask that you:

* Coordinate with the Provider before publishing public, high-visibility benchmarks or detailed "under-the-hood" technical reviews (e.g., blog posts or public video essays).
* Refrain from sharing internal logic schemas or non-public documentation.

